1
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:06,360
Hinata, time to eat.

2
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:19,280
You were on the track team, weren't you?

3
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,840
Look who's talking.

4
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,120
I heard you were fast.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,000
I just never joined any clubs.

6
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,440
You're a 'go-home club' member too, right?

7
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:36,000
Back in my second year...

8
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,920
I injured my leg.

9
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,280
Ah, it hurts!

10
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:51,520
Hey! Are you okay? Is it your knee?

11
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:55,160
I couldn't make it back to the team, so I just quit.

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,880
Does that mean you can never run again?

13
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,680
Who knows?

14
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,680
But, if it's a relay race...

15
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,920
Maybe I could give it a shot.

16
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:12,160
But...

17
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,160
Someone who's injured...

18
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,120
Would only be a burden to everyone else.

19
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,400
Hinata.

20
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,680
Do you want to run?

21
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,200
Huh?

22
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,800
Well...

23
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,520
I love running.

24
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:37,080
Then go for it.

25
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,200
But that wouldn't be right.

26
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:46,240
Besides, it would just worry everyone.

27
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:49,400
If I run and we lose...

28
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:52,160
Everyone will be so disappointed.

29
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,560
You're too worried about what others think.

30
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,120
Hiding your true feelings isn't the answer.

31
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,880
Even if you fail...

32
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,160
It's a relay race.

33
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,880
I'll make up for it for you.

34
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,320
So I'm saying...

35
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,880
Stop acting like my big brother!

36
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:15,400
I really don't get you sometimes.

37
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,600
What do you want to do?

38
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,000
I...
